      <title>特朗普就任总统后，美元创一年来最长涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/dollar-set-for-longest-run-of-gains-in-a-year-amid-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的总统胜利和持续的经济增长推动交易员推高美元，美元正在创下一年多以来最长的周度涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/dollar-set-for-longest-run-of-gains-in-a-year-amid-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 10:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
